---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---
<MainLayout title="Sustainability - Eco-Friendly Ideas to Loved Products" description="We prioritize sustainable practices in every step, turning ideas into eco-conscious, durable everyday products people love and value long-term. Explore our commitment to responsible creation.">



<!-- Sustainability at the Core ‚Äì Exact Vertical Card Layout -->
<section class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-gradient-to-b from-green-50/50 to-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto space-y-16 md:space-y-20 lg:space-y-24">

    <!-- Main Headline with Plant Icon -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-4 md:gap-6">
        <h2 class="
          text-3xl xs:text-3xl sm:text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl
          font-black tracking-wide leading-none text-gray-900
        ">
          SUSTAINABILITY
        </h2>
        <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="text-green-600 text-6xl md:text-8xl">‚ôªÔ∏è</span>
          <span class="text-green-700 text-5xl md:text-7xl">üå±</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="
        mt-4 text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl
        font-black text-blue-600 tracking-wide
      ">
        AT THE CORE
      </h3>

      <p class="
        mt-6 text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl
        text-gray-700 font-medium max-w-4xl mx-auto leading-relaxed
      ">
        Our commitment to innovation goes hand in hand with care for the planet.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Vertical Stacked Cards (exactly one below another) -->

    <!-- Card 1: Product Development -->
    <div class="
      bg-white border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-2xl
      shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
      overflow-hidden flex flex-col lg:flex-row
    ">
      <!-- Left Image -->
      <div class="lg:w-5/12 h-64 lg:h-auto">
        <img
          src="/images/reserved-designs-product-development-sustainability.avif"
          alt="Sustainable product development ‚Äì eco materials and prototyping"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>

      <!-- Right Content -->
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center lg:w-7/12">
        <h4 class="
          text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
          font-black text-blue-700 mb-4 md:mb-6
        ">
          PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT ‚ôªÔ∏è
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8">
          Sustainability in product development begins with thoughtful planning. We integrate eco-conscious materials, efficient design, and minimal waste processes from concept to production. This approach not only reduces environmental impact but creates products that are durable, responsible, and future-ready.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <a
            href="/product-development"
            class="
              inline-block bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700
              text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl
              transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg
              text-lg md:text-xl
            "
          >
            LEARN MORE ABOUT PRODUCT DEVELOPMENT
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2: Web Design -->
    <div class="
      bg-white border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-2xl
      shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
      overflow-hidden flex flex-col lg:flex-row
    ">
      <div class="lg:w-5/12 h-64 lg:h-auto">
        <img
          src="/images/reserved-designs-website-development-sustainability.avif"
          alt="Sustainable web design ‚Äì low-carbon, green hosting"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center lg:w-7/12">
        <h4 class="
          text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
          font-black text-blue-700 mb-4 md:mb-6
        ">
          WEB DESIGN ‚ôªÔ∏è
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8">
          Sustainable web design focuses on building efficient, fast, low-energy websites hosted on green servers. We optimize performance, reduce digital carbon footprints, and create lasting experiences that minimize the need for frequent redesigns and resource waste.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <a
            href="/web-design"
            class="
              inline-block bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700
              text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl
              transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg
              text-lg md:text-xl
            "
          >
            LEARN MORE ABOUT WEB DESIGN
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3: Graphic Design -->
    <div class="
      bg-white border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-2xl
      shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
      overflow-hidden flex flex-col lg:flex-row
    ">
      <div class="lg:w-5/12 h-64 lg:h-auto">
        <img
          src="/images/reserved-designs-graphic-designing-sustainability.avif"
          alt="Sustainable graphic design ‚Äì eco materials & digital-first"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center lg:w-7/12">
        <h4 class="
          text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
          font-black text-blue-700 mb-4 md:mb-6
        ">
          GRAPHIC DESIGN ‚ôªÔ∏è
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8">
          We embrace sustainable graphic design by reducing unnecessary printing, choosing eco-friendly materials, and designing for digital-first experiences. Every decision considers sustainability ‚Äî from color choices to production methods ‚Äî ensuring our creative work supports the planet.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <a
            href="/graphic-design"
            class="
              inline-block bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700
              text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl
              transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg
              text-lg md:text-xl
            "
          >
            LEARN MORE ABOUT GRAPHIC DESIGN
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 4: CAD Design -->
    <div class="
      bg-white border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-2xl
      shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
      overflow-hidden flex flex-col lg:flex-row
    ">
      <div class="lg:w-5/12 h-64 lg:h-auto">
        <img
          src="/images/reserved-designs-cad-design-sustainability.avif"
          alt="Sustainable CAD design ‚Äì precise, waste-reducing modeling"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center lg:w-7/12">
        <h4 class="
          text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
          font-black text-blue-700 mb-4 md:mb-6
        ">
          CAD DESIGN ‚ôªÔ∏è
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8">
          Our CAD processes minimize waste before production begins. Using precise digital models, we reduce trial-and-error, saving materials and energy. We integrate eco-friendly principles into every stage of design, ensuring smarter, cleaner production.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <a
            href="/cad-design"
            class="
              inline-block bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700
              text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl
              transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg
              text-lg md:text-xl
            "
          >
            LEARN MORE ABOUT CAD DESIGN
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 5: 3D Printing -->
    <div class="
      bg-white border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-2xl
      shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
      overflow-hidden flex flex-col lg:flex-row
    ">
      <div class="lg:w-5/12 h-64 lg:h-auto">
        <img
          src="/images/reserved-designs-3d-printing-sustainability.avif"
          alt="Sustainable 3D printing ‚Äì biodegradable materials"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center lg:w-7/12">
        <h4 class="
          text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
          font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4 md:mb-6
        ">
          3D PRINTING ‚ôªÔ∏è
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8">
          3D printing allows precise manufacturing with reduced waste. We use biodegradable filaments and recyclable materials whenever possible, supporting a circular production model that minimizes environmental impact.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <a
            href="/3d-printing"
            class="
              inline-block bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700
              text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl
              transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg
              text-lg md:text-xl
            "
          >
            LEARN MORE ABOUT 3D PRINTING
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 6: Wood Craftsmanship -->
    <div class="
      bg-white border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-2xl
      shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl transition-all duration-300
      overflow-hidden flex flex-col lg:flex-row
    ">
      <div class="lg:w-5/12 h-64 lg:h-auto">
        <img
          src="/images/reserved-designs-wood-craftsmanship-sustainability.avif"
          alt="Sustainable wood craftsmanship ‚Äì eco-sourced timber"
          class="w-full h-full object-cover"
          loading="lazy"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="p-6 md:p-8 lg:p-10 flex flex-col justify-center lg:w-7/12">
        <h4 class="
          text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl
          font-bold text-blue-700 mb-4 md:mb-6
        ">
          WOOD CRAFTSMANSHIP ‚ôªÔ∏è
        </h4>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6 md:mb-8">
          We source sustainably harvested wood and repurpose materials whenever possible. Our craftsmanship aims to reduce waste, prolong product life, and maintain ecological balance ‚Äî ensuring every piece contributes positively to the planet.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-auto">
          <a
            href="/services/wood-crafts"
            class="
              inline-block bg-pink-600 hover:bg-pink-700
              text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-xl
              transition-all duration-300 shadow-md hover:shadow-lg
              text-lg md:text-xl
            "
          >
            LEARN MORE ABOUT WOOD CRAFTSMANSHIP
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>



  
</MainLayout>
